data.description: 4-Bedroom, 2-Bath Home in Time Square Village. Modern elegance meets convenience in this pristine, well-loved like-new home. With neutral grays and beautiful granite throughout, it offers a soothing and luxurious ambiance. Enjoy four bedrooms, two modern bathrooms, a spacious 3-car garage, and a beautiful Austin stone wood-burning fireplace in the living room. Located near shopping, dining, and top-rated schools. Don't miss this gem!
